Class JarGenruleDescription

    public class JarGenruleDescription
extends AbstractGenruleDescription<JarGenruleDescriptionArg>
implements ImplicitDepsInferringDescription<JarGenruleDescriptionArg>
    Based on GenruleDescription except specialized to produce a jar.

    The produced jar behaves similarly to a jar produced by java_binary, which means it can be executed by buck run or using the $(exe ) macro.
